OL,5, Tesco has become the latest supermarket
OL,6, to increase pay as retailers face up to
OL,7, the rising minimum wage and try to     
OL,8, retain staff.                          
OL,10,FThe hourly pay rate for store workers  
OL,11,Fwill rise from #11.02 to #12.02 in     
OL,12,FApril, while pay for workers in London 
OL,13,Fwill rise to #13.15 an hour.           
OL,15,FMore than 200,000 staff will benefit   
OL,16,Ffrom the increase, Tesco said.         
OL,18,FAll staff will get the voluntary Real  
OL,19,FLiving Wage, which is higher than the  
OL,20,Fcompulsory National Living Wage.       
